### **Q2. `[KTU University Exam - May 2024]`**
**List any three differences between Linked and Indexed file allocation. Which one is used by the UNIX `inode` system?**

> **Model Answer (3 Marks):**

| S.No. | Linked Allocation | Indexed Allocation |
